---
<section class="roastery">
  <img
    class="roastery-img"
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1442512595331-e89e73853f31?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80"
    alt="Mesin roasting kopi batch di Rimbun Roastery Bandung"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <div class="roastery-over">
    <div class="roastery-content fu">
      <span class="label">Roastery Process</span>
      <h2 class="disp-lg">Dari Green Bean<br />ke Cangkirmu</h2>
      <p>
        Kami roasting dalam batch kecil (max 5kg) setiap hari Senin dan Kamis.<br />
        Kopi yang sampai ke tanganmu tidak pernah lebih dari 7 hari sejak roast date.
      </p>
      <div class="roastery-badges">
        <div class="r-badge"><strong>5kg</strong><small>Max per batch</small></div>
        <div class="r-badge"><strong>7 hari</strong><small>Freshness guarantee</small></div>
        <div class="r-badge"><strong>2×</strong><small>Roasting / minggu</small></div>
        <div class="r-badge"><strong>100%</strong><small>Traceable origin</small></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
